# Knowledge Base Format

Each item in the Ask Pulau Brani knowledge base should be reviewed before use.

## Recommended fields

- `source_id`: Unique ID, e.g. `PB-KB-001`
- `title`: Title of source
- `source_type`: Oral history, article, photograph, recipe, map, book excerpt, transcript
- `community_review_status`: Pending, reviewed, approved, restricted
- `public_use`: Yes / No / Limited
- `summary`: Short summary
- `key_topics`: Main themes
- `related_places`: Places mentioned
- `related_people`: People mentioned, if approved
- `sensitivity`: Public, review needed, restricted, private
- `citation`: How the source should be cited
- `approved_text`: Text the chatbot may use

## Rule

Only `approved_text` from sources marked `public_use: Yes` or `public_use: Limited` should be used by the chatbot.
